snippet.title: Xbox LIVE Arcade - N+
snippet.description:
In a futuristic world of inadvertently homicidal robots, a daring ninja must use deft acrobatic skill and guts of steel to survive. Play N+, one of the nominated titles in the 2008 Arcade Awards. 

Find out more about N+ here:
http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/games/media/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d8025841085c/?cid=SN_CRM_YT_XBLA_030409_NP

Find out how to vote for your favorite Xbox LIVE Arcade tite:
http://www.xbox.com/en-US/community/events/xblaawards/?cid=SN_YTMar09_AWDS08

Rated Everyone 10+
